{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong><i>Last Hopper</i></strong>, you play as the last combat hopper with a big mission: clear your homeland of invading spiders and other insects! Your  ant buddy has come prepared with a shotgun (yeah, an ant with a shotgun!), and together, you\u2019ll jump, dodge, and blast through waves of enemies to save your fellow grasshoppers. Every time you fire, the shotgun\u2019s wild recoil blasts you backward, giving every jump and shot a wacky, tactical twist. And don\u2019t forget to grab a snack! Munch on mushrooms and berries scattered around to keep up your strength.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ant Buddy with a Shotgun</strong>: This ant\u2019s not just tagging along\u2014he\u2019s packing heat and ready to help you in the fight!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Booming Shotgun Recoil</strong>: Fire off a shot and get blasted backward! Use this to your advantage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Merchant</strong>: Earn  currency by killing enemies, visit  merchant to get upgrades and fun perks because every combat hopper needs cool gear!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fast-Paced, Hoppy Fun</strong>: Jump into action, shoot through danger, and defend your homeland in a silly, speedy adventure.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730908814","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802500/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730908814","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802500/4423ca4f7dbc71d5d69826449aca90efc8c11750/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730908814","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802500/4423ca4f7dbc71d5d69826449aca90efc8c11750/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730908814","cat